Mischa Hausserman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mischa_Hausserman 0 Mischa Hausserman (born October 31, 1941) is an Austrian-born American film and television actor. Hausserman was born in Vienna, Austria. He had moved to the United States in 1965. He studied acting at the Herbert Berghof Studios and then went on to New York University.
